    <style>
        :root {
            --primary: #9b87f5;
            --primary-glow: rgba(155, 135, 245, 0.2);
            --bg: #0f0e10;
            --text: #ffffff;
            --text-secondary: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.6);
            --card-bg: #141318;
            --border-1: #18191c;
            --border-2: #222327;
        }

        * {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
        }

        body {
            background: var(--bg);
            color: var(--text);
            font-family: 'Poppins', sans-serif;
            height: 100vh;
            width: 100vw;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
            overflow: hidden;
        }

        .bg-grid {
            position: fixed;
            top: 0;
            left: 0;
            width: 100%;
            height: 100%;
            background-image: radial-gradient(circle at 2px 2px, var(--primary) 1.4px, transparent 0);
            background-size: 34px 34px;
            opacity: 0.12;
            z-index: -1;
            mask: radial-gradient(circle at center, black 35%, transparent 70%);
            animation: gridPulse 3s ease-in-out infinite;
        }

        @keyframes gridPulse {
            0% {
                opacity: 0.08;
            }

            50% {
                opacity: 0.25;
            }

            100% {
                opacity: 0.08;
            }
        }

        .container {
            width: 100%;
            max-width: 380px;
            padding: 0 1rem;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            align-items: center;
        }

        .logo {
            font-size: 2.2rem;
            font-weight: 600;
            margin-bottom: 2rem;
            position: relative;
            letter-spacing: -0.5px;
            background: linear-gradient(180deg, #ffffff, rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.75));
            -webkit-background-clip: text;
            background-clip: text;
            color: transparent;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 0.6rem;
        }

        .logo .ls {
            color: var(--primary);
            position: relative;
        }

        .brand-mark {
            width: 32px;
            height: 32px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            display: inline-block;
            flex-shrink: 0;
            box-shadow: 0 6px 20px rgba(0,0,0,0.35);
            border: 1px solid var(--border-1);
        }

        .logo .underline {
            position: absolute;
            bottom: -5px;
            left: 0;
            width: 100%;
            height: 8px;
        }

        .logo .underline path {
            stroke: var(--primary);
            stroke-width: 8;
            fill: none;
            stroke-dasharray: 410;
            stroke-dashoffset: 410;
            animation: drawLine 1.5s forwards ease;
        }

        @keyframes drawLine {
            to {
                stroke-dashoffset: 0;
            }
        }

        .card {
            width: 100%;
            background: var(--card-bg);
            backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
            border-radius: 12px;
            padding: 1.5rem;
            position: relative;
            overflow: hidden;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 30px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.25);
        }

        @keyframes gradientExpandFromCenter {
            0% {
                transform: scaleX(0);
                opacity: 0;
            }

            100% {
                transform: scaleX(1);
                opacity: 1;
            }
        }

        .card::before {
            content: '';
            position: absolute;
            inset: 0;
            border-radius: 12px;
            border: 1px solid var(--border-1);
            pointer-events: none;
        }

        .card::after {
            content: '';
            position: absolute;
            inset: 0;
            border-radius: 12px;
            border: 1px solid var(--border-2);
            transform: translateY(1px);
            pointer-events: none;
        }

        .card-header::after {
            content: '';
            display: block;
            height: 1px;
            margin-top: 1rem;
            background: linear-gradient(90deg, transparent, rgba(255,255,255,0.06), transparent);
        }

        .card-header {
            margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
        }

        .card-title {
            font-size: 1rem;
            font-weight: 500;
            margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
        }

        .card-title::before {
            content: '';
            display: inline-block;
            width: 4px;
            height: 16px;
            background: linear-gradient(180deg, var(--primary), rgba(155,135,245,0.6));
            margin-right: 8px;
            border-radius: 2px;
            box-shadow: 0 0 20px var(--primary-glow);
        }

        .card-subtitle {
            color: var(--text-secondary);
            font-size: 0.8rem;
            font-weight: 300;
        }

        .captcha-box {
            min-height: 70px;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
            position: relative;
        }

        .captcha-box::after {
            content: '';
            position: absolute;
            bottom: -10px;
            left: 0;
            width: 100%;
            height: 1px;
            background: linear-gradient(90deg,
                    transparent 0%,
                    rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1) 50%,
                    transparent 100%);
        }

        .ray-info {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            font-size: 0.7rem;
            color: var(--text-secondary);
            font-family: ui-monospace, SFMono-Regular, Menlo, Monaco, Consolas, "Liberation Mono", "Courier New", monospace;
        }

        @keyframes fadeIn {
            from {
                opacity: 0;
            }

            to {
                opacity: 1;
            }
        }

        .container {
            animation: fadeIn 0.5s ease forwards;
        }

        @media (max-width: 480px) {
            .logo {
                font-size: 1.8rem;
            }

            .card {
                padding: 1.25rem;
            }
        }
    </style>
